<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A9204005001">
<title>
Discharge Headlight System
</title>
<ptxt>
When any of the following problems is detected, the ballasts respond to it for fail-safe control, causing operation of the discharge headlights to stop.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
In the case of discharge headlight problem, determine areas for inspection using the following table.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "1.059in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.794in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "1.587in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.758in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Problem
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Problem Detail
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Fail-safe Control
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Condition for Canceling Fail-safe Control
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Open output voltage circuit
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Defect in connection between discharge headlight bulb and igniter
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Poor igniter connector connection
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Open circuit between ballast and igniter
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Defective discharge headlight bulb
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Ballast stops operating within 1 second after detection of problem.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Lighting switch: “OFF”
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Shorted output voltage circuit
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Short circuit between ballast and igniter
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Defective discharge headlight bulb
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</servinfosub>
